<L>__{exterior residence, stairs night}
<A>__{with a soldier on either side of him, the dalai lama descends the staircase. the soldiers start to lead him away, but he pauses.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{wait.}
<A>__{the young man leaves them.}
<L>__{exterior residence night}
<A>__{he walks to the far side of this white building.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{i see a safe journey.}
<A>__{the boy returns to the front steps.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{i see a safe return.}
<A>__{the soldiers wait.}
<C>__{tenzin gyatso}
<D>__{now. i am ready.}
<A>__{tenzin gyatso places the scroll over one shoulder. a soldier lays a rifle over the other one.}
